post_text: Be sure to purchase your tickets at each school for the 2nd Annual Student Art Gallery and Spring Musical on Thursday, May 11, 2017 at Rich South High School. The Student Art Gallery will begin at 6:00 p.m. followed by the Spring Musical at 7:00 pm. Not only do we have a great show planned, you will not want to miss the world premiere of the Unbreakable video composed, written and edited by Country Club Hills School District 160 students! We look forward to seeing you there!
